babysitters.name: hamida2
babysitters.about: Hello to all inquires. My name is Jaida Morris, I am 19 years old and I am passionate about reading, painting, writing, music and even photography. I love children and believe that they are the gateway to heaven. I spent time watching kids for most of my life that includes cousins, nieces, nephews and even kids I didn’t know. I love children … any child is a safe child with me.
